<paragraph id="IFRS09_BC6.553"><paranum>BC6.553</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 9 BC"/><data name="paranum" value="BC6.553"/></prolog><body><p>In September 2019 the IASB amended <ph outputclass="standard_ref"><ph outputclass="standard_number">IFRS 9</ph></ph>, <ph outputclass="standard_ref"><ph outputclass="standard_number">IAS 39</ph></ph> and <ph outputclass="standard_ref"><ph outputclass="standard_number">IFRS 7</ph></ph> by issuing <i>Interest Rate Benchmark Reform</i>, which confirmed with modifications the proposals in the 2019 Exposure Draft. In the amendments issued in September 2019, the IASB added <xref href="IFRS09_g6.8.1-6.8.12.dita">paragraphs 6.8.1&#x2013;6.8.12</xref> and <xref href="IFRS09_7.1.8.dita" scope="local">7.1.8 to <ph outputclass="standard_ref"><ph outputclass="standard_number">IFRS 9</ph></ph></xref> and amended <xref href="IFRS09_7.2.26.dita#IFRS09_7.2.26">paragraph 7.2.26 of <ph outputclass="standard_ref"><ph outputclass="standard_number">IFRS 9</ph></ph></xref>.</p></body></paragraph>